data.description: This stunning colonial-style house is now available for sale, offering an array of desirable features and an ideal location just minutes away from the Garden State Parkway and famous Jersey Shore beaches. Basting a spacious interior and a range of modern amenities, this home is perfect for comfortable family living and entertaining guests. This property offers a unique opportunity for those with a business, as it is zoned B3 and features side parking for convenience. The oversized 80x132 lot provides plenty of space to accommodate various needs and preferences. This is a rare opportunity to own a stunning colonial-style home with an abundance of features and upgrades including a new roof in 2021.
